OL,3,CWoman arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cattempted murder in Westminster
OL,6,FA woman has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof attempted murder after a car hit
OL,8,Fpedestrians in central London in the
OL,9,Fearly hours of Sunday morning.
OL,11,FA woman in her 30s is in hospital in a
OL,12,Fcritical condition and a man in his
OL,13,F50s suffered life-changing injuries
OL,14,Fafter they were hit by a car in Argyll
OL,15,FStreet, Westminster, at around 4.30am
OL,16,Fon Sunday, the Metropolitan Police
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,FA second woman in her 30s also
OL,20,Fsuffered minor injuries, the force
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
