OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776687066
OL,3,CWoman arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cattempted murder in Westminster
OL,6,FThe driver of the car, a 29-year-old
OL,7,Fwoman, was arrested at the scene on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of attempted murder,
OL,9,Fgrievous bodily harm, dangerous
OL,10,Fdriving and drink driving and taken
OL,11,Finto custody.
OL,13,FPolice say the incident, which took
OL,14,Fplace on a Soho street home to the
OL,15,FLondon Palladium theatre, is not being
OL,16,Ftreated as terrorism-related.
OL,18,FDetective chief inspector Alison
OL,19,FFoxwell called for potential witnesses
OL,20,Fto come forward.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
