OL,3,CWoman arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cattempted murder in Westminster
OL,6,F"As our inquiries continue, our
OL,7,Fthoughts are with those injured and
OL,8,Ftheir loved ones.
OL,10,F"While this incident took place in the
OL,11,Fearly hours of the morning, venues in
OL,12,Fthe area were still open, and we
OL,13,Fbelieve a number of people will have
OL,14,Fseen what happened.
OL,16,F"I would urge anyone who witnessed the
OL,17,Fcollision, or any activity prior to it
OL,18,Fthat they feel may be of relevance, to
OL,19,Fcome forward.
